Hey, what are you doing here!?
(Would you like Sabrina to throw the block down?)
Hey, what are you doing here!?
\n<Adam>Yeah lucky for you, you have a magic fire. Im putting a heater in this thing next.
\n<Adam>What are they guarding in here anyways?
(ADAM opens a box and finds frozen patties. He opens another and finds more frozen meat.)
\n<Sabrina>Its just food? So what is this their personal fridge.
\n<Adam>Looks like it, but we can guess they didnt buy all this.
\n<Sabrina>Yeah look theres a box from Magic Burger
(There is a loud bang. They see that a large metal door opens. They see a man with a deer head.)
\n<YOUSEF>What do you mean some of the outside guards are missing!?
\n<Grunt>Um, they probably went to get food without telling us again...
\n<YOUSEF>So, Get them back here before I kick all of your asses!
\n<YOUSEF>I swear, if I get in trouble and VAL stick me with more boring work, I am pumble
(he grunt runs off and YOUSEF slams his office door.)
\n<Adam>We should be careful though. You just dont become in charge of a warehouse for no
\n<Charles>Hey guys, how are you all holding up? Sorry I had to give a statement to the police
\n<Charles>Sorry I wasn't chatting. I got a follow up call about the shops robbery.
\n<Charles>Back to the matter at hand. It's great you all got in!
\n<Adam>Great timing actually. We got some more info, this isn't their only base and
\n<Sabrina>Oh, and the guy here is a big buff blue deer guy. He looks familiar...
\n<Charles>Hmm... I might be able to find something.
\n<Charles>Hmmm, I dont see anything connecting a VAL with Dark Wings. Must be a
nickname. But I did find something about a man with a blue deer head.
(CHARLES send a picture to ADAM. ADAM pulls it up on his gauntlets using his holograms. It
\n<Sabrina>Yeah, thats him! Woah, I didnt recognize him with that mask on.
\n<Sabrina>Yeah, his name is YOUSEF YOUNG. He used to be a pro boxer, but he got banned
\n<Charles>Yeah, he was also found guilty of murder but charges were dropped.
\n<Adam>Oh Jeez...So, um, what is he doing working for Dark Wings?
\n<Charles>Well, thats for us to figure out. You guys should probably get him somewhere
alone. I dont think it would be wise to take him on with backup.
Got it, well see what we can do.
Im sure we can take him.
Got it, well see what we can do.
Im sure we can take him.
\n<Sabrina>Yeah! Dont worry. I know we can take him. I know all his moves!
\n<Sabrina>Pftt, we got this dude. Dont worry so much.
\n<Charles>Alright, Ill let you guys focus for now. Call me if you need anything. I will
keep researching see if I find anything. Good luck!
(SABRINA gets up to leave. ADAM doesnt move and shakes.)
Just worried we might get hurt.
Just a bit nervous. Thats all.
Its fine, I just need to get back in the game.
Just worried we might get hurt.
\n<Sabrina>Hey, whos the one who protected you since we were kids? I got your back.
Just a bit nervous. Thats all.
\n<Sabrina>Hey, weve gotten this far havent we? We can handle this. Me and you together.
Its fine, I just need to get back in the game.
\n<Sabrina>Alright if you say so. But Im here for you.
(SABRINA pats ADAM on the back. ADAM takes a deep breath and exhales.)
\n<Adam>Now lets take everyone down and try not to get caught.
\n<Adam>Oof, the cold didnt make that easy but we got them all.
\n<Sabrina>Yeah, you see we could do it!
\n<Adam>Yeah, but wasnt it a bit too easy for my liking.
(YOUSEF comes out of his office room.)
(YOUSEF points at them. He then jumps toward them and starts to run to them. SABRINA and ADAM
(ADAM gets blasted by a puff of cold air and gets launched into a wall. SABRINA moves her
direction to YOUSEF and blocks a punch. ADAM gets up and dusts off the frost on his armor.
\n<Adam>But alright, that the last time I get thrown into a wall.
(ADAM finds a trash lid and uses it as a makeshift shield.)
(YOUSEF dodges one of SABRINAs punches. He then uses this opening to punch her in the gut
and sends her flying into a wall.)
\n<YOUSEF>I mean that was the plan but you two are tougher than expected. Either way, are
you guys Knights or something like that?
\n<Adam>Yeah, something like that. We just wanna know who your boss is.
\n<YOUSEF>Yeah, like Ill tell you guys that info.
(SABRINA ignites her fist and gets in a ready stance.)
\n<YOUSEF>Yeah, Ill like to see you try.
(YOUSEF lets out a large exhale and gets into a boxer stance.)
(ADAM slams his fist into the trash can lid to break off the ice.)
\n<Charles>Alright guys, here is your first real fight. Brace yourselves!
(ADAM and SABRINA stand opposite to YOUSEF. They are all panting. ADAM holds his left arm
which is bleeding due to some icicles. Sabrina is bleeding from her forehead. One Hay-Hay
has flopped on ADAMs right shoulder. Another is clutched to his leg. The last one is being
held under SABRINAs arm. YOUSEF holds his rib cage.)
First one to passout buys the other one lunch.
I think- we need a new strategy - ow.
\n<Sabrina>Good, SILVER- I got enough magic left for a few more rounds. How about you?
\n<Adam>Good, I still got power left in my suit.
First one to passout buys the other one lunch.
\n<Sabrina>Now youre on! You think you can keep up with him Mr. SILVER?
\n<Adam>Yeah, I have enough power to take him down.
I think- we need a new strategy - ow.
\n<Sabrina>I dunno hitting him hard seems to be working well. What do you want to do?
\n<Adam>I dunno, we go for his leg?
\n<Charles>Are you sure? You guys look pretty bad.
Yeah, weve lasted this long. Cant run now.
Even if we do run, this guy isnt gonna let us leave here alive.
I think yeah we might need to retreat for now.
Yeah, weve lasted this long. Cant run now.

\n<Charles>I know but you guys need to at least try

\n<YOUSEF>You guys finally gave me a good fight. No one has ever lasted this long. You
\n<Sabrina>Thanks, Ill put it on my resume.
\n<Adam>Just give up, its pointless at this point.
(YOUSEF starts running towards ADAM and SABRINA.)
(ADAM and SABRINA brace themselves. In the middle of his run, YOUSEF gets sudden pain in
his chest. He coughs up blood. He falls face forward and slides towards ADAM and SABRINA.
He shakily lifts up his arm then lets it go. It lands on ADAMs foot.)
\n<Adam>We should help him out. We still need to question him. Plus we cant just let him
die. MONITOR, can you help us out here?
\n<Charles>Yeah, you guys should heal up first though. Cant have you guys passing out too.
Ill go ahead and leave an anonymous tip to the authorities.
(YOUSEF wakes up in shock. He tries to move but he is tied with rope and bended metal pipes.
ADAM and SABRINA stand over him.)
\n<YOUSEF>Well, it looks like I lost this fight.
\n<Adam>Alright, tell us what you know. We won fair and square.
(YOUSEF tries to free himself but stops after he gets the pain back in his lung.)
\n<Adam>Yeah, I wont do that if I were you. We patched you up the best we could but we
Why does Dark Wing hate Knights?
\n<YOUSEF>Your guess is as good as mine. They just give me orders.
\n<YOUSEF>Oh, this is just one of our food supplies.
\n<YOUSEF>I dunno. I just watch this one.
Why does Dark Wing hate Knights?
\n<YOUSEF>Hell if I know. I just joined so I could fight them.
\n<YOUSEF>There are just a bunch of stuck up pricks. Theyll get whats coming to them.
Do all of you plan to take down the Knights?
Do all of you plan to take down the Knights?
\n<YOUSEF>this all you got!? These are some simple questions. You guys could have figured
